## DESCRIPTION
## Arithmetic Sequences
## ENDDESCRIPTION

## KEYWORDS('sequence')

## DBsubject(Algebra)
## DBchapter(Finite sequences and series)
## DBsection(Recursive)
## Date('05/05/2026')
